-- Anheuser-Busch InBev Plans Russia Wastewater Plant, Novosti Says
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2012-11-02T17:03:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-02/anheuser-busch-inbev-plans-russia-wastewater-plant-novosti-says.html
Anheuser-Busch InBev NV (ABI)  plans to
invest about 100 million rubles ($3.2 million) to construct a
wastewater treatment facility at its Ivanovo brewery in the
Moscow region, Novosti said, citing a spokesperson for InBev’s
Russian unit, Sun InBev. The project on completion will help
reduce the plant’s negative impact on the environment, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
